CustomField.formula:
/*If an Academic Program exists for the Opportunity, retrieve the associated School/College from the Academic Program Account*/
IF(NOT(ISBLANK(Academic_Program__c)),(  Academic_Program__r.Department__r.Name  ),

/*IF not, retrieve the associated School/College from the Recruitment Program Account on the Opportunity*/
(  Recruitment_Program__r.Department__r.Name  ))
